#titlebar("Kim Jones" "" "" "purple")
&lt;br&gt;
__Chairman, Board of Directors__
&lt;br&gt;
With more than 20 years in the technology industry, Kim Jones brings with her a wealth of experience in various senior leadership positions. As the Chairman of Curriki's Board of Directors, Jones will assist the company in reaching its goal of making quality learning and the infrastructure to support it universally accessible.

Jones is currently Vice President of Global Education, Government and Health Sciences at Sun Microsystems. Prior to this role, Jones was the Vice President of Global Education and Research and established Education as an independent Line of Business for Sun. Jones is active in driving policy initiatives, as evidenced by her testimony before the Congressional Web based Education Commission. She is also a frequent speaker on the impact of technology in education at influential meetings around the world.

Jones graduated with honors with a Bachelors of Arts degree from University of California, San Diego.

</content></xwikidoc>